For card transaction information, other than the monthly statement, go online to the: Search tab on the red bar >> Transaction Query >> Transaction Details.

You’ll enter a date range in the first section, and then in the second section you can search by a card number, driver ID, etc.; or if you just click on Search without filtering, you’ll see all the transactions on your account for that period.

